MAMA CASS ELLIOT - RARITIES COLLECTION (FLAC)

This collection includes lossless FLAC rips of the following:

1. CASS ELLIOT - (Self-Titled) LP album
2. ROAD IS NO PLACE FOR A LADY - LP album
3. THE MUGWUMPS - CD
4. THE COMPLETE CASS ELLIOT SOLO COLLECTION 1968-71 - Double-CD collection* 

High-quality scanned artwork is included for all of the above.  

* A 2005 release including all the tracks from the original albums "Bubble Gum, Lemonade & Something For Mama" and "Dream a Little Dream" (the latter not to be confused with recent anthology CDs released under the same title), plus many previously unreleased tracks and singles.  Artwork is also included for the original LPs, even though the corresponding audio files were ripped from the new 2-CD set for maximum quality.
